Summary of modifications
------------------------

- Added CKS coverage and two CKA mock exams weighted to the published exam
  blueprint.
- Rewrote worked solutions to an imperative-first workflow.
- Added Georgian localisation for the interface, lab catalogue and all questions.
- Rebuilt the landing page around the lab catalogue.
- Replaced the deprecated desktop base image, made all images build locally, and
  added a self-hosted desktop base.
- Fixed graders that could never fail, tasks that were unsatisfiable on the
  bundled cluster, and a number of platform defects in networking, resource
  limits and the remote desktop.
- Added scripts/lint-exams.py to catch these classes of defect before merge.

See FIXES.md for the detailed change log.
